<div class="switchable__text">
<h2>Seamless file uploads</h2>
<p class="lead">
When you have a busy day you need to know the file hosting system you are using is on-hand at all times. Our Uploadfiles app is designed to monitor your local folder of choice for updates made throughout the day. That means whenever a file or folder is added or modified, it is automatically uploaded to your Uploadfiles account. Once installed you don’t have to do anything else beyond ensuring the app is running in the background and we’ll take care of the rest.
<br><br>
For added ease of use, you can simply drag and drop files directly into our files share system via the app icon in Windows, or the app tray icon on Mac. Your data is instantly backed up in multiple locations in our secure cloud system so you never have to worry about data loss again.

</div>
