<div class="col-md-6 col-lg-5">
<div class="switchable__text">
<h2>One click copy & share</h2>
<p class="lead">
To check the progress of files uploading or syncing, all you have to do is check the app window where you can see the progress of each file upload as you drag and drop them into the queue. Once complete, just click the link icon to instantly copy a shareable file URL to your clipboard. Then you can share the link with whoever else you may need to access the upload in the future.
<br><br>
Each file upload is also assigned its own unique 15 digit hash. This security is put in place to further protect your files so only those given permission to access the file can do so. We know how important privacy is to you online, which is why we go above and beyond to protect your data from start to finish.
</p>

</div>
